title: For Richer Or Poorer (1997).avi
description:
For Richer or Poorer is a (1997) comedy film starring Tim Allen and Kirstie Alley.

Plot: The incredibly rich, but miserable New York couple, Brad and Caroline Sexton, got framed by their accountant, and fled from the IRS to the one place where noone would look for them: Amish country. Now they've got to do their best to blend in, and learn how to love all over again.
